incident_updates.body: Start time : 13/06/2022 09:26 UTC Service impact : Slowness observed on some hosted websites on filerz1580 Technical impact (DC/geographical area) : GRA1 Scope of impact : All offers on cluster028 Ongoing actions : Our technical teams investigate to determine the origin of the incident
The migration of the cluster is still in progress. We will come back to you when the migration is completed.

Update:Our teams are in the process of migrating the data to a different filerz which takes time. That's why the regeneration of statistics is suspended. We will come back to you when the migration is completed.
Update: There are ongoing maintenance tasks that prevent the regeneration of statistics. The regeneration of statistics will normally take place mid-next week.

The regeneration of stats is still on its way.
We will post update when significant progress has been made.

Update:We are restarting the last generation for the rest of customer.

Update: Our teams will finish generating 50% on the 13/03/2022. We will keep you informed of the progress.

Update: Our technical teams have detected a bug making the display of the statuses invisible on a date period higher than 1 month. They are investigating to determine the origin

Start time : 27/04/2022 04:18 UTC Service impact : Statistics are no longer generated from 27 April 2022 Technical impact (DC/geographical area) : GRA2 Scope of impact : All offers on cluster006 are unavailable.
